    <string name="settings_digital_rec_title">Assisted recording</string>
    <string name="settings_digital_rec_desc">Simplify sticks and triggers for more consistent recordings</string>
    <string name="settings_digital_rec_info">When enabled, stick and trigger inputs are simplified to discrete values while recording.\n\nSticks snap to configurable directions + neutral, and triggers become binary.\n\nPrecision will be reduced, but your recordings will replay much more consistently — ideal for repeatable routines.\n\nTap the gear icon to fine-tune each stick.\n\nOnly applies while you are actively recording.</string>
